<mf:PropertyAppraisal1> <mf:hasRemarks> """Parking Type and Condition of Spaces: Adequate for Subject Improvements. Condition: Average Type: 101 asphalt paved and striped parking spaces, including 5 ADA compliant handicap designated spaces

Additional Amenities: Coin laundry in Office Building""" .

<mf:PropertyAppraisal1> <mf:hasRemarks> """Functional Utility: Average

Design & Appeal: Average. Design, functional utility and appeal rated as average as compared to most competing properties in the market.""" .

